钟南山团队发表新筛查方式：15分钟出结果。
Zhong Nan Shan team released the new screening method: 15 minutes to produce results.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
王忠耀/@光明日报@光明日报 3月11日消息，近日，钟南山院士团队叶枫课题组在《医学病毒学杂志》在线发表论文，初次描述了IgM-IgG联合抗体检测试剂的研发，以及在新冠病毒感染性疾病临床诊断中的应用。
In a recent online paper published in the Journal of Medical Virology, the team of academicians, Ye Feng, first described the development of IgM-IgG joint antibody detection reagent and its application in clinical diagnosis of new crown virus infection.
据介绍，该检测试剂滴血可验，约15分钟就能出结果，大大缩短了检测的时间（病毒核酸RT-PCR检测需要3-4小时出结果）。
According to the report, the test reagent drip blood, about 15 minutes can produce results, greatly reducing the detection time (viral nucleic acid RT-PCR test takes 3-4 hours results).
多中心的临床标本检测评价证实，该检测试剂临床检测的敏感性高达88.66%，检测特异性为90.63%；IgM-IgG联合抗体检测的敏感性远高于IgM或IgG单抗体检测。
The multi-center clinical specimen test evaluation confirmed that the sensitivity of the detection reagent was 88.66% and the detection specificity was 90.63%; the sensitivity of IgM-IgG was much higher than that of IgM or IgG single antibody.
另外，该抗体检测试剂采用指尖血与静脉血检测结果作对比，发现两者检测的一致性基本吻合，提示这一联合抗体快速检测试剂盒可用作即时检测，可在床旁用指尖采血方式进行检测。
In addition, the antibody detection reagent used fingertip blood and venous blood test results, found that the two tests are basically consistent, suggesting that this joint antibody rapid detection kit can be used for instant detection, can be used in the bed with fingertips blood collection methods.
